<br>
<br>
And lastly, perhaps the most coveted piece of Guardian in the whole of Norrath, is the elegant yet simple Guardian Robe. When you first look at the stats, you might think; ah, just another caster's robe, why should a big barsher like myself be interested in such a thing?<br>
<br>
Now this is where the sheer beauty of being on a PvP server comes into play. Say you are a DE Shadowknight. You head into Skyshrine when there are lighties about. You put on your robe and equip your Mace of the Shadowed Souls, then sit down an pretend to meditate. (This is especially fun if you have your harmtouch up). Some lightie comes by and think, &quot;Aha! A low mana cleric, this should be easy!&quot; Ahh.. I can hear the screams of surprise and dismay now!<br>
<br>
This is a pretty rare drop, and this is definitely an item that we want all of our casters to get first, but it's certainly a nice item for any class to acquire. <br>
